  <span class="italic">ii</span>) degree-weighted average, and (
  <span class="italic">iii</span>) eigenvector-based average.
 </p>
 <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Does our reduced 2D system capture some basic properties of real bipartite mutualistic networks? Treating the effective mutualistic interaction strengths (
