    </div>
   </div>
  </div>) as two independent parameters in the reduced model, we calculate the effective pollinator and plant abundances for each pair of the parameters. In the 3D plot of an effective species abundance vs. 
  <div class="inline-formula">
   <div id="i37" class="math">
